column1: PREFIX prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>  DESCRIBE ?kaviri from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   ?kaviri  rdfs:label "Kaviri"@en . }

PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbres: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1>   SELECT  ?team ?nflid ?wiki from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  dbres:Sam_Shields dbpprop:currentteam ?team .  dbres:Sam_Shields dbpprop:nfl ?nflid .  ?wiki foaf:primaryTopic dbres:Sam_Shields . }

PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbres: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>   SELECT  ?team ?nflid ?wiki from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  OPTIONAL {dbres:Sam_Shields dbpprop:currentteam ?team .}  OPTIONAL {dbres:Sam_Shields dbpprop:nfl ?nflid .}   OPTIONAL {?wiki foaf:primaryTopic dbres:Sam_Shields .}  }

SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {     ?v0   a   <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/SoccerClub>.   { ?v0  <http://dbpedia.org/property/ground>  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain>.  } UNION  { ?v0  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/ground>  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain>.  }   } limit 10

SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?e <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/series> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sopranos> . ?e <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/releaseDate> ?date . ?e <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/episodeNumber> ?number . } order by desc(?date)

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Fritz Lang"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Fritz Lang"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Pierre Le Rouzic"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Pierre Le Rouzic"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {<http://dbpedia.org/resource/C&M_Airways> ?p ?v. optional { ?v rdfs:label ?lbl. filter(lang(?lbl)="" || langmatches(lang(?lbl),"EN")) } optional { ?v dbpprop:occupation ?occ. filter(lang(?occ)="" || langmatches(lang(?occ),"EN")) } } order by ?p

SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {<http://dbpedia.org/resource/C&M_Airways> ?p ?v. optional { ?v rdfs:label ?lbl. filter(lang(?lbl)="" || langmatches(lang(?lbl),"EN")) } optional { ?v dbpprop:occupation ?occ. filter(lang(?occ)="" || langmatches(lang(?occ),"EN")) } } order by ?p

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Daniel Cohen"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Daniel Cohen"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX geo: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX foaf:<http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>  SELECT  DISTINCT ?title ?page ?lat ?long from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {?link rdfs:label ?title; foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?page; geo:lat ?lat; geo:long ?long . FILTER (regex(?title, "^Tokyo$","i") && lang(?title) = 'en') }

PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/>   SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   ?name rdf:type yago:NationalBasketballAssociationTeams . } LIMIT 10

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?name ?birth ?death ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {      ?person dbo:birthPlace :Berlin .      ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth .      ?person foaf:name ?name .      ?person dbo:deathDate ?death .      FILTER (?birth < "1900-01-01"^^xsd:date) . } ORDER BY ?name

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>  SELECT  DISTINCT * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {  ?country rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Country .    ?country dcterms:subject ?subject .    ?country2 rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Country .    ?country2 foaf:name "Uruguay"@en .    ?country2 dcterms:subject ?subject .  }

SELECT  distinct ?member from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {      {         ?member dc:subject category:Members_of_the_United_States_House_of_Representatives .     } union {         ?member dc:subject [skos:broader category:Members_of_the_United_States_House_of_Representatives] .     }      ?member a db:Person . }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?p a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Philosopher> . ?p <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/influenced> ?influenced. }

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>  SELECT  DISTINCT * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {  ?country a dbpedia-owl:Country ;    dcterms:subject ?subject .    ?country2 foaf:name "Uruguay"@en .    ?country2 dcterms:subject ?subject .  }

SELECT  ?uri ?name from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbpedia-owl:University . ?uri foaf:name ?name . } LIMIT 1000 OFFSET 1000
SELECT  ?uri ?name from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbpedia-owl:University . ?uri foaf:name ?name . } LIMIT 1000 OFFSET 2000
SELECT  ?uri ?name from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbpedia-owl:University . ?uri foaf:name ?name . } LIMIT 1000 OFFSET 6000

PREFIX property: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX geo: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX foaf:<http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>  SELECT  DISTINCT ?page ?lat ?long from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {?link property:name ?name; rdfs:label ?title; foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?page; geo:lat ?lat; geo:long ?long . FILTER (regex(?name, "Tokyo", "i") || regex(?name, "Tokyo", "i"))}

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?person ?bio from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?person dbo:birthPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pittsburgh> ;         rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/AmericanBloggers> ;         dbo:abstract ?bio . }

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>    SELECT  (count(?date) as ?count) ?film ?date1  {     ?film dbo:starring ?actor .     ?film rdf:type dbo:Film .     ?film dbo:releaseDate ?date .     ?film dbo:releaseDate ?date1 .     ?film dbo:country dbr:United_States .      FILTER( xsd:date(?date) > "2000"^^xsd:date )  } HAVING ?count=1 LIMIT 10

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?comp from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE{ ?c rdfs:label ?comp . ?c a dbpedia:ontology/Company  } limit 10

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>    SELECT  ?film ?date1  {     ?film dbo:starring ?actor .     ?film rdf:type dbo:Film .     ?film dbo:releaseDate ?date .     ?film dbo:releaseDate ?date1 .     ?film dbo:country dbr:United_States .      FILTER( xsd:date(?date) > "2000"^^xsd:date )  } HAVING count(?date)=1 LIMIT 10

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>    SELECT  ?film ?date1  {     ?film dbo:starring ?actor .     ?film rdf:type dbo:Film .     ?film dbo:releaseDate ?date .     ?film dbo:releaseDate ?date1 .     ?film dbo:country dbr:United_States .      FILTER( xsd:date(?date) > "2000"^^xsd:date )  } GROUP BY ?film HAVING count(?date)=1 LIMIT 10

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  DISTINCT ?person ?name ?birthDate ?photo from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   ?person ont:birthDate ?birthDate .   ?person rdfs:label ?name .    ?person a <http://umbel.org/umbel/rc/Artist> . column1: PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbres: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>   SELECT  ?x, str(?showNameB) AS ?showName, str(?countryB) AS ?country, str(?languageB) AS ?language, str(?runtimeB) AS  ?runtime, str(?numberOfEpisodesB) AS  ?numberOfEpisodes, str(?firstAiredB) AS ?firstAired, str(?lastAiredB) AS ?lastAired, str(?owlStarringB) AS ?owlStarring, str(?propStarringB) AS ?propStarring  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  {?x dbpedia-owl:genre dbres:Telenovela} UNION {?x dbpedia-owl:format dbres:Telenovela}.  OPTIONAL {?x dbpprop:showName ?showNameB}.  OPTIONAL { ?x dbpedia-owl:country ?countryB}.  OPTIONAL { ?x dbpedia-owl:language ?languageB}.  OPTIONAL { ?x dbpedia-owl:runtime ?runtimeB}.  OPTIONAL { ?x dbpedia-owl:numberOfEpisodes ?numberOfEpisodesB}.  OPTIONAL { ?x dbpprop:firstAired ?firstAiredB}.  OPTIONAL { ?x dbpprop:lastAired ?lastAiredB}.  OPTIONAL { ?x dbpedia-owl:starring ?owlStarringB}.  OPTIONAL { ?x dbpprop:starring ?propStarringB}. FILTER (     ?firstAiredB >= "2012-01-01"^^xsd:date &&     ?firstAiredB <= "2012-12-30"^^xsd:date   )  }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?isValueOf from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   { ?isValueOf <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://schema.org/MusicGroup> } }
PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?country  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {       ?country dbpedia-owl:Location ?euope }
SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?s ?p ?o   ?o a owl:Thing.  ?s a owl:Thing. }  ORDER BY ?s OFFSET 0 LIMIT 10
SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?s ?p ?o.  ?o a owl:Thing.  ?s a owl:Thing. }  ORDER BY ?s OFFSET 0 LIMIT 10

PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?country  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {       ?country dbpedia-owl:continent dbpedia:Europe }
SELECT  distinct ?p1 from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?s a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Scientist>. ?s <http://dbpedia.org/property/name> ?name. FILTER regex(?name,'Einstein','i'). } LIMIT 100

SELECT  ?name ?birth ?death ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?person birthPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin> . ?person birthDate ?birth . ?person foaf:name ?name . ?person deathDate ?death FILTER (?birth < "1900-01-01"^^xsd:date) . } ORDER BY ?name LIMIT 10

SELECT  ?s ?p ?o from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?s ?p ?o.  ?o a owl:Thing.  ?s a owl:Thing.  ?s rdfs:label ?label1.  ?o rdfs:label ?label2.  FILTER(langMatches(lang(?label1), "EN"))  FILTER(langMatches(lang(?label2), "EN")) }  OFFSET 0 LIMIT 10

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Ang Lee"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Ang Lee"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Ang Lee"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Ang Lee"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Ang Lee"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Ang Lee"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}
SELECT  distinct ?mj from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {?mj ?p "Magic Johnson"} limit 10

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Iceberg Slim"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Iceberg Slim"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?s ?o from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?s rdfs:label ?o ; ?s rdf:type <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Person>.  } limit 100

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?s ?o from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  { ?s rdfs:label ?o ; ?s rdf:type foaf:Person .  }  limit 100

PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?name ?birth ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?person dbpedia2:birthPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin> . ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth . ?person foaf:name ?name } ORDER BY ?name LIMIT 10

SELECT  *  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE   { ?town <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/populationTotal> ?populationTotal; <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?label . FILTER(langMatches(lang(?label), "EN"))  } ORDER BY DESC(?populationTotal)

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX d: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>   SELECT  ?book ?authorName ?bookName  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   ?book d:publisher :Penguin_Group .   ?book d:author ?author .    ?book rdfs:label ?bookName .    ?book dbpedia2:genre :Historical_novel .   ?author rdfs:label ?authorName . FILTER ( lang(?bookName) = "en") FILTER ( lang(?authorName) = "en")  } ORDER BY ?authorName
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>    SELECT  ?personen  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?person dbp:deathplace dbr:Darmstadt }

PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>         PREFIX dbp-ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>         PREFIX dbp-prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>         PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>         prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>         prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>         prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>         PREFIX : <http://verticalsearchworks.com/rdf/>         Select *          from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE         {            Service <http://dbpedia.org/sparql>         {           bind (dbp-ont:BasketballPlayer as ?athleteClass)           ?athlete a ?athleteClass          }         }         limit 10

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?property ?hasValue ?isValueOf from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise> ?property ?hasValue }   UNION   { ?isValueOf ?property <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise> } }
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>  SELECT  ?promi from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?promi dbp:birthPlace dbr:Darmstadt }

PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>         PREFIX dbp-ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>         PREFIX dbp-prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>         PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>         prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>         prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>         prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>         PREFIX : <http://verticalsearchworks.com/rdf/>         Select *          from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE         {           Bind(dbp-ont:BasketballPlayer as ?athleteClass)           ?athlete a dbp-ont:BasketballPlayer         }         limit 10

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Béatrice Fontanel"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Béatrice Fontanel"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}

PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>    SELECT  ?dinge  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?dinge     ?beziehung dbr:Darmstadt.         ?dinge     ?beziehung2 dbr:Frankfurt. }

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX swrc: <http://swrc.ontoware.org/ontology#>   SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?ResearchPaper1 rdf:type swrc:ResearchPaper . ?ResearchPaper1 swrc:author ?Person1 . ?Person1 rdf:type swrc:Person .}  LIMIT 100

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT
column2: distinct ?person   from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {

column1: PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX swrc: <http://swrc.ontoware.org/ontology#>   SELECT  ?ResearchPaper1 from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?Person1 rdf:type swrc:Person . ?ResearchPaper1 swrc:author ?Person1 . ?ResearchPaper1 rdf:type swrc:ResearchPaper .}  LIMIT 100

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?p a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Person> . ?p <dbpedia-owl:birthYear> ?birthYear. ?p <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/influenced> ?influenced. ?influenced a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Person>. }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?author }
SELECT  distinct ?Authors from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {publication a ?ResearchPaper} LIMIT 100

PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>         PREFIX dbp-ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>         PREFIX dbp-prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>         PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>         prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>         prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>         prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>         PREFIX : <http://verticalsearchworks.com/rdf/>         Select distinct *         from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE         {           ?athlete a dbp-ont:BasketballPlayer;             dbp-prop:name ?name.           Optional           {             ?athlete dbp-ont:abstract ?abstract.              Filter (langMatches(lang(?abstract),"en"))            }           Optional           {             ?athlete dbp-ont:team ?team.           }            Optional           {             ?athlete dbp-ont:careerStart ?careerStart.                }           Optional           {             ?athlete dbp-ont:careerEnd ?careerEnd.                }           }         limit 20

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  distinct ?group from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   ?group a dbpedia-owl:Group .   ?group dbpprop:locationCity ?name .   FILTER contains(?name, "london") }  LIMIT 5

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?entity ?label (MAX(?score) AS ?score1)  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE{ ?entity <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?label. (?label ?score) pf:textMatch 'Galway'. } GROUP BY ?entity ?label ORDER BY DESC(?score1) LIMIT 3

PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>         PREFIX dbp-ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>         PREFIX dbp-prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>         PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>         prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>         prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>         prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>         PREFIX : <http://verticalsearchworks.com/rdf/>         Select distinct *         from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE         {           ?athlete a dbp-ont:BasketballPlayer;             dbp-prop:name ?name.           Optional           {             ?athlete dbp-ont:abstract ?abstract.              Filter (langMatches(lang(?abstract),"en"))            }           Optional           {             ?athlete dbp-ont:team ?team.             ?team a ?teamType.             Filter(?teamType = <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/NationalBasketballAssociationTeams>)           }           Optional           {             ?athlete dbp-prop:cteam ?cteam.           }           Optional           {             ?athlete dbp-ont:careerStart ?careerStart.                }           Optional           {             ?athlete dbp-ont:careerEnd ?careerEnd.                }           }         limit 10

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>         PREFIX type: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>   SELECT  ?EUcountries ?ginicoefficient ?government from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {                    ?EUcountries rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Country .              ?EUcountries skos:broader category:Member_states_of_the_European_Union .              prop:gini ?ginicoefficient ;              prop:governmentType ?government .      FILTER (?ginicoefficient >= 34 && langMatches(lang(?country_name), "EN")) . }

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Dave Filoni"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Dave Filoni"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Paolo Conte"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Paolo Conte"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>         PREFIX type: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>   SELECT  ?EUcountries ?ginicoefficient ?government from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {                    ?EUcountries rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Country ;              rdfs:label ?country_name ;                           prop:gini ?ginicoefficient ;              prop:governmentType ?government .      FILTER (?ginicoefficient >= 34 && langMatches(lang(?country_name), "EN")) . }

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>         PREFIX type: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>   SELECT  ?EUcountries ?ginicoefficient ?government from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {                    ?EUcountries rdf:type skos:Concept ;              rdfs:label ?country_name ;                  skos:prefLabel: ?Member states of the European Union ;                       prop:gini ?ginicoefficient ;              prop:governmentType ?government .      FILTER (?ginicoefficient >= 34 && langMatches(lang(?country_name), "EN")) . }

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>         PREFIX type: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>   SELECT  ?EUcountries ?ginicoefficient ?government from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {                    ?EUcountries rdf:type skos:Concept ;              rdfs:label ?country_name ;                  skos:prefLabel ?Member states of the European Union ;                       prop:gini ?ginicoefficient ;              prop:governmentType ?government . PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?title ?value from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   {      ?country ?prop ?uri.      ?country a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Country>.      ?country rdfs:label ?label.      ?prop rdf:type rdf:Property.      ?prop rdfs:label ?title.      ?uri rdfs:label ?value.      FILTER (lang(?value) = "en")   } UNION   {     ?country ?prop ?value.      ?country a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Country>.      ?country rdfs:label ?label.      ?prop rdf:type rdf:Property.      ?prop rdfs:label ?title.   } FILTER (?label = "United States"@en && !isURI(?value)) }

FILTER (lang(?value) = "en")  }

FILTER (?label = "United States"@en && lang(?value) = "en")   }   UNION   SELECT  ?title ?value from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE   {     ?country ?prop ?value.      ?country a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Country>.      ?country rdfs:label ?label.      ?prop rdf:type rdf:Property.      ?prop rdfs:label ?title.      FILTER (?label = "United States"@en && !isURI(?value))   } }

column1: PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?subject <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Car_manufacturers>. } LIMIT 20

FILTER (?population > 15000000) }

FILTER (?population > 15000000) }

column1: PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?name ?birth ?death ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {      ?person dbo:birthPlace :Berlin .      ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth .      ?person foaf:name ?name .      ?person dbo:deathDate ?death .      FILTER (?birth < "1900-01-01"^^xsd:date) . } ORDER BY ?name

PREFIX prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> ASK {   <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_River> prop:length ?amazon .   <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nile> prop:length ?nile .   FILTER(?amazon > ?nile) . }

SELECT  ?event ?date ?definition     FROM <http://dbpedia.org>      from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {         {           ?event dbpedia-owl:date ?date . FILTER ( ?date >= xsd:date("18990101") && ?date <= xsd:date("19000101") )             } UNION {           ?event dbpprop:date ?date . FILTER ( ?date >= xsd:date("18990101") && ?date <= xsd:date("19000101") )           ?event dbpedia-owl:abstract ?definition .             }         } LIMIT 20000

SELECT  ?event ?date ?definition     FROM <http://dbpedia.org>      from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {         {           ?event dbpedia-owl:date ?date . FILTER ( ?date >= xsd:date("18990101") && ?date <= xsd:date("19000101") )           ?event dbpedia-owl:abstract ?definition . FILTER langMatches( lang(?definition), ?en’) }             } UNION {           ?event dbpprop:date ?date . FILTER ( ?date >= xsd:date("18990101") && ?date <= xsd:date("19000101") )           ?event dbpedia-owl:abstract ?definition . FILTER langMatches( lang(?definition), ?en’) }             }         } LIMIT 20000

SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {     ?v0   a   <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/University>.   { ?v0  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/province>  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany>.  } UNION  { ?v0  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country>  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany>.  } UNION  { ?v0  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/state>  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany>.  } UNION  { ?v0  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/campus>  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany>.  } UNION  { ?v0  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/city>  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany>.  }   }

FILTER (?name = ?something) .  } LIMIT 5

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?name ?birth ?death ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {      ?person dbpedia2:birthPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin> .      ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth .      ?person foaf:name ?name .      ?person dbo:deathDate ?death      FILTER (?birth < "1900-01-01"^^xsd:date) . }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?subject ?label ?released ?abstract from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?subject rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film>. ?subject dbpedia2:starring <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise>. ?subject rdfs:comment ?abstract. ?subject rdfs:label ?label. FILTER(lang(?abstract) = "en" && lang(?label) = "en"). ?subject <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/releaseDate> ?released. FILTER(xsd:date(?released) < "2000-01-01"^^xsd:date). } ORDER BY ?released LIMIT 20

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX geo: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#>  SELECT  ?subject ?label ?lat ?long from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eiffel_Tower> geo:lat ?eiffelLat. <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eiffel_Tower> geo:long ?eiffelLong. ?subject geo:lat ?lat. ?subject geo:long ?long. ?subject rdfs:label ?label. FILTER(?lat - ?eiffelLat <= 0.05 && ?eiffelLat - ?lat <= 0.05 && ?long - ?eiffelLong <= 0.05 && ?eiffelLong - ?long <= 0.05 && lang(?label) = "en" ). } LIMIT 20

column1: # algemene namespace definities PREFIX dcterms:  <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX categorie: <http://nl.dbpedia.org/resource/Categorie:> PREFIX sjabloon: <http://nl.dbpedia.org/resource/Sjabloon:> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://nl.dbpedia.org/property/>   SELECT  ?wikipagina, ?concept from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {    #  SELECT eeer alle pagina's met categorie "Nederlands schrijver"   ?concept  dcterms:subject  categorie:Nederlands_schrijver .    # haal de naam van de oorspronkelijk Wikipedia pagina op   ?concept foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?wikipagina    # filter de records die alleen maar de categorie "Nederlands schrijver" hebben   # records met meerdere categorieen komen dus niet in deze lijst    FILTER NOT EXISTS {      ?concept dcterms:subject ?categorie     filter(str(?categorie) !=  'http://nl.dbpedia.org/resource/Categorie:Nederlands_schrijver')   }    # kijk of er op deze pagina een infobox sjabloon gebruikt is   OPTIONAL {     ?concept dbpedia:wikiPageUsesTemplate ?sjabloon . SELECT  ?s1 as ?place SAMPLE(?name) as ?name SAMPLE(?lat) as ?lat SAMPLE(?long) as ?long SAMPLE(?page) as ?page SAMPLE(?kind) as ?kind MAX(?area) as ?area from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?s1 foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?page FILTER regex(?page,"^http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zurich") . ?s1 foaf:name ?name . OPTIONAL {{?s1 geo:lat ?lat } UNION {?s1 dbpprop:latitude ?lat}} . {{?s1 geo:long ?long } UNION { ?s1 dbpprop:longitude ?long}}. OPTIONAL { ?s1 a ?kind FILTER (?kind = <http://schema.org/Country> || ?kind = <http://schema.org/City> || ?kind = <http://schema.org/AdministrativeArea>)} . OPTIONAL { {?s1 dbpedia-owl:areaTotal ?area} UNION { ?s1 dbpprop:totalarea ?area} } . } GROUP BY ?s1

prefix rdfs: <http://www.3w.org/2001/01/rdf-schema#> prefix tbl:<http://www.w3.org/People/Berners-Lee/card#> prefix foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> prefix karl:<http://www.w3.org/People/karl/karl-foaf.xrdf#>  SELECT  ?personName2 ?predicate ?object From <http://www.w3.org/People/Berners-Lee/card> From <http://www.w3.org/People/karl/karl-foaf.xrdf> From <http://www.koalie.net/foaf.rdf> From <http://heddley.com/edd/foaf.rdf> From <http://www.cs.umd.edu/~hendler/2003/foaf.rdf> From <http://www.dajobe.org/foaf.rdf> From <http://www.isi.edu/~gil/foaf.rdf> From <http://www.ivan-herman.net/foaf.rdf> From <http://www.kjetil.kjernsmo.net/foaf> From <http://www.lassila.org/ora.rdf> From <http://www.mindswap.org/2004/owl/mindswappers> from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE{   tbl:i foaf:know ?person. ?person foaf:name ?personName1;    rdfs:seeAlso ?iri. ?iri foaf:primaryTopic ?person2. ?person2 foaf:name ?personName2;   ?predicate ?object Filter(?personName1=?personName2).    }

column1: PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?name ?birth ?death ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {      ?person dbo:birthPlace :Berlin .      ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth .      ?person foaf:name ?name .      ?person dbo:deathDate ?death .      FILTER (?birth < "1900-01-01"^^xsd:date) . } ORDER BY ?name

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Henri Gougaud"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Henri Gougaud"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?film from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?film <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:French_films> }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX quepy: <http://www.machinalis.com/quepy#> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  DISTINCT * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   ?x0 rdf:type foaf:Person.   ?x0 rdfs:label "Wilhelm Georg Gustav Botho Rudolf Hans Reichsfreiherr von BoineburgLengsfeld"@en.   ?x0 rdfs:comment ?x1. }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?name ?birth ?death ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {      ?person dbpedia2:birthPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin> .      ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth .      ?person foaf:name ?name .      ?person dbo:deathDate ?death      FILTER (?birth < "1900-01-01"^^xsd:date) . }

SELECT  DISTINCT * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {<http://dbpedia.org/resource/amsterdam> ?property ?object.FILTER ((( isIRI(?object) && ?property != <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/depiction> )|| ?property = <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label>  || ?property = <http://www.georss.org/georss/point> || ?property = <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/surname> || ?property = <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/name> || ?property = <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title>))}  ORDER BY ?property
SELECT  DISTINCT *  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {{<http://dbpedia.org/resource/amsterdam> ?property ?object. FILTER(!isLiteral(?object))} UNION
column2: {<http://dbpedia.org/resource/amsterdam> ?property

column1: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX onto: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>  SELECT  DISTINCT ?uri ?string from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {         ?uri rdf:type yago:MonarchsOfTheUnitedKingdom .         { ?uri onto:spouse ?spouse . } UNION { ?spouse onto:spouse ?uri . }         ?spouse onto:birthPlace res:Germany.         OPTIONAL {?uri rdfs:label ?string. FILTER (lang(?string) = 'en') } }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?subject ?label ?released ?abstract from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?subject rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film>. ?subject dbpedia2:starring <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise>. ?subject rdfs:comment ?abstract. ?subject rdfs:label ?label. FILTER(lang(?abstract) = "en" && lang(?label) = "en"). ?subject <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/releaseDate> ?released. FILTER(xsd:date(?released) < "2000-01-01"^^xsd:date). } ORDER BY ?released LIMIT 20

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Ettore Scola"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Ettore Scola"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

PREFIX owl:<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX rdf:<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs:<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbpedia-owl:<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  SELECT      ?drugname     ?indication from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?drug     a    dbpedia-owl:Drug . ?drug     rdfs:label    ?drugname . ?drug     owl:sameAs    ?drugbank . }

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Douglas Preston"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Douglas Preston"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}

SELECT  ?country, ?code, ?code2 from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {     ?country a dbpedia-owl:Country.     ?code dbpedia-owl:wikiPageRedirects ?country.         filter regex(str(?code), '^http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISO_3166-1:[A-Z]{2}$') .     BIND(REPLACE(str(?code), '/ISO_3166-1:', '/ISO_3166-2:', "i") AS ?code2)  } LIMIT(100)

PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbres: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>   SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  ?y rdf:type dbpedia-owl:ChemicalCompound.  ?y rdfs:label ?Name .  OPTIONAL {?y dbpedia-owl:iupacName ?iupacname} .  OPTIONAL {?y dbpprop:tradename ?tradename}.  OPTIONAL {?x dbpedia-owl:wikiPageRedirects ?y}.  OPTIONAL {?y dcterms:subject ?y1}  FILTER (langMatches(lang(?Name),"en"))  } limit 10000 OFFSET  90000

SELECT  ?country, ?code, ?code2, ?code21 from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {     ?country a dbpedia-owl:Country.     ?code dbpedia-owl:wikiPageRedirects ?country.         filter regex(str(?code), '^http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISO_3166-1:[A-Z]{2}$') .     BIND(REPLACE(str(?code), '/ISO_3166-1:', '/ISO_3166-2:', "i") AS ?code2) .     ?code21 dbpedia-owl:wikiPageRedirects ?code2   } LIMIT(100)

SELECT  ?country, ?code, ?code2, ?code21 from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {     ?country a dbpedia-owl:Country.     ?code dbpedia-owl:wikiPageRedirects ?country.         filter regex(str(?code), '^http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISO_3166-1:[A-Z]{2}$') .     BIND(REPLACE(str(?code), '/ISO_3166-1:', '/ISO_3166-2:', "i") AS ?code2)      ?code21 dbpedia-owl:wikiPageRedirects ?code2   } LIMIT(100)

SELECT  ?country, ?code, ?code2, ?code21  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {     { ?country a dbpedia-owl:Country.       ?code dbpedia-owl:wikiPageRedirects ?country.           filter regex(str(?code), '^http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISO_3166-1:[A-Z]{2}$') .       BIND(REPLACE(str(?code), '/ISO_3166-1:', '/ISO_3166-2:', "i") AS ?code2)      }       ?code21 dbpedia-owl:wikiPageRedirects ?code2   } LIMIT(100)
SELECT  distinct ?Concept from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {[] a ?Concept  } LIMIT 100
SELECT  distinct ?d from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {?d dbpedia:subject dbpedia:the_matrix}

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?subject <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:National_Basketball_Association_teams>. }
Select distinct ?code from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?code a rdf:ISO_3166-2 }

PREFIX dbpedia_prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>  PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>   PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>   PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>   PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>   PREFIX dbpedia_ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   PREFIX lcx: <http://schemars.samsung.com/ontologies/media/contentfabric/2013/3/lcx#>   CONSTRUCT { <http://user1> foaf:interest  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Ship> . ?ships rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Ship>. ?ships dbpedia_ont:builder ?shipYards; foaf:name ?name; dbpedia_ont:abstract ?abstract; dbpedia_ont:thumbnail ?thumbnail. ?shipYards dbpedia_prop:location <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richmond,_California> }  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?ships rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Ship>.  ?ships dbpedia_ont:builder ?shipYards.  ?ships foaf:name ?name.  ?ships dbpedia_ont:abstract ?abstract.  ?shipYards dbpedia_prop:location <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richmond,_California>.  OPTIONAL { ?ships dbpedia_ont:thumbnail ?thumbnail } } LIMIT 1

PREFIX dbpedia_prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>  PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>   PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>   PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>   PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>   PREFIX dbpedia_ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   PREFIX lcx: <http://schemars.samsung.com/ontologies/media/contentfabric/2013/3/lcx#>   CONSTRUCT { <http://user1> foaf:interest  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Ship> . ?ships rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Ship>. ?ships dbpedia_ont:builder ?shipYards; foaf:name ?name; dbpedia_ont:abstract ?abstract; dbpedia_ont:thumbnail ?thumbnail. ?shipYards dbpedia_prop:location <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richmond,_California> }  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?ships rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Ship>.  ?ships dbpedia_ont:builder ?shipYards.  ?ships foaf:name ?name.  ?ships dbpedia_ont:abstract ?abstract.  ?shipYards dbpedia_prop:location <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richmond,_California>.  OPTIONAL { ?ships dbpedia_ont:thumbnail ?thumbnail } } LIMIT 1
Select distinct ?code, ?item from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {      ?code dbpprop:iso ?item     FILTER regex(?code, '\\w{2,}-\\w{1,3}', "i") }

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Sofi Oksanen"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Sofi Oksanen"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>  PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  ?x rdfs:label 'Steven Spielberg'@en.  ?x dbprop:occupation ?occupation.  FILTER (LANG(?abstract) = 'en')  } limit 1
SELECT  distinct ?prop  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {?prop rdf:type rdf:Property } LIMIT 100
SELECT  distinct ?prop  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {     ?prop rdf:type rdf:Property      FILTER regex(str(?prop), '.?\\\w*iso\w*$',"i") } LIMIT 100
SELECT  distinct ?dbpedia-owl:award from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {[] a ?dbpedia-owl:award} LIMIT 100

Select distinct ?code, ?item from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {      { ?item dbpprop:iso ?code }     UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isocode ?code }     UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isodistrict ?code }      UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166Code ?code }     UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166code ?code }     UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCode ?code }     UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCodeRegion ?code }     UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoRegion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoSubcode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoregion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isosubcode ?code }     FILTER regex(?code, "^\\w{1,2}-\\w{1,3}", "i") } order ?code, ?item

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Michel Peyramaure"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Michel Peyramaure"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

Select distinct ?code # , ?item  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {   {     { ?item dbpprop:iso ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isocode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isodistrict ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166Code ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166code ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCodeRegion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoRegion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoSubcode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoregion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isosubcode ?code }     FILTER regex(?code, "^\\w{1,2}-\\w{1,3}$", "i")  }  FILTER regex(?code, "^US-", "i") } ORDER BY ?code # ?item

Select distinct count(?code) # , ?item  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {   {     { ?item dbpprop:iso ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isocode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isodistrict ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166Code ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166code ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCodeRegion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoRegion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoSubcode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoregion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isosubcode ?code }     FILTER regex(?code, "^\\w{1,2}-\\w{1,3}$", "i")  }  FILTER regex(?code, "^US-", "i") } ORDER BY ?code # ?item

Select count(distinct ?code) # , ?item  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {   {     { ?item dbpprop:iso ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isocode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isodistrict ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166Code ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166code ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCodeRegion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoRegion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoSubcode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoregion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isosubcode ?code }     FILTER regex(?code, "^\\w{1,2}-\\w{1,3}$", "i")  }  FILTER regex(?code, "^US-", "i") } ORDER BY ?code # ?item

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Jacques Brel"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Jacques Brel"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Jacques Brel"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Jacques Brel"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}

Select distinct ?code, ?item  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE  {   {     { ?item dbpprop:iso ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isocode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isodistrict ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166Code ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:iso3166code ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoCodeRegion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoRegion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoSubcode ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isoregion ?code }  UNION     { ?item dbpprop:isosubcode ?code }     FILTER regex(?code, "^\\w{1,2}-\\w{1,3}$", "i")  }  # FILTER regex(?code, "^US-", "i") } ORDER BY ?code ?item

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?p from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg> dbprop:occupation ?p }

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbpedia-owl:   <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  SELECT  ?p from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/  Steven_Spielberg> dbpprop:occupation ?p

PREFIX rdfs:<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>  PREFIX dbpedia-owl:<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?p from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Spielberg> dbpprop:occupation ?p

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Jean Van Hamme"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Jean Van Hamme"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>     PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>    PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>    PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>    PREFIX dbprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>    PREFIX dbcat: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:>    PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>      SELECT  DISTINCT ?poet ?poet_name ?surname ?poet_wiki_link ?abstract     from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE     {  ?poet dcterms:subject dbcat:book ;        foaf:name ?poet_name ;        foaf:surname ?surname ;        dbpedia-owl:abstract ?abstract ;        foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?poet_wiki_link .      FILTER ( lang(?abstract) = "en" )    } ORDER BY ?surname       LIMIT 20 OFFSET 0

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Jean Ferrat"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Jean Ferrat"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influences ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influenced ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influenced ?auteur.}}.?influence rdf:type dbpedia-owl:Person.?influence dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?influenceDateBirth.{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences }.FILTER (LANG(?Influences ) = "fr")}

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?film from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?film <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:French_films> }

PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>     PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>    PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>    PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>    PREFIX dbprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>    PREFIX dbcat: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:>    PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>      SELECT  DISTINCT ?poet ?poet_name ?surname ?poet_wiki_link ?abstract     from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE     {  ?poet dcterms:subject dbcat:American_poets ;        foaf:name ?poet_name ;        foaf:surname ?surname ;        dbpedia-owl:abstract ?abstract ;        foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?poet_wiki_link .      FILTER ( lang(?abstract) = "en" )    } ORDER BY ?surname       LIMIT 20 OFFSET 0

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  distinct ?book from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?book a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/book> } LIMIT 10

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  distinct ?book from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?book a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Work> "tolkien" } LIMIT 10
SELECT  distinct ?Concept from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {[] a ?Concept} LIMIT 100

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  distinct ?book from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?book a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Book> } LIMIT 10

PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>   SELECT  ?player ?name ?team ?dob ?number ?place_of_birth ?weight COALESCE(?prop_position, ?owl_position) AS ?position COALESCE(?o_debut_team, ?p_debut_team) AS ?debut_team ?debut_year ?active_years_end_year from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   ?team <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:National_Football_League_teams>. ?player rdfs:label ?name . ?player dbpedia-owl:team ?team . OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:position ?owl_position } . OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:number ?number} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpprop:currentpositionplain ?prop_position} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:birthDate ?dob} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:debutTeam ?o_debut_team} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpprop:debutteam ?p_debut_team}. OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:weight ?weight} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:height ?height} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpprop:placeOfBirth ?place_of_birth} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpprop:debutyear ?debut_year}. OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:activeYearsEndYear ?active_years_end_year}.  FILTER(lang(?name) = 'en') } LIMIT 100
