column1: prefix dbpo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> prefix foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>  SELECT  distinct ?title, ?pict, ?label, ?abstract from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {<http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius_Marius> dbpo:title ?title ; foaf:depiction ?pict ; rdfs:label ?label ; dbpo:abstract ?abstract FILTER ( lang(?abstract) = "en" )}

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  DISTINCT  ?player { ?s foaf:page ?player. ?s rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/SoccerPlayer> . ?s dbpedia2:position ?position . ?s <http://dbpedia.org/property/clubs> ?club . ?club <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/capacity> ?cap . ?s <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> ?place . ?place ?population ?pop. OPTIONAL {?s <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/number> ?tricot.} Filter (?population in (<http://dbpedia.org/property/populationEstimate>, <http://dbpedia.org/property/populationCensus>, <http://dbpedia.org/property/statPop> )) Filter (xsd:int(?pop) >10000000 ) . Filter (xsd:int(?cap) >40000 ) . Filter (?position = "Goalkeeper"@en || ?position = <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goalkeeper_%28association_football%29> || ?position = <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goalkeeper_%28football%29>) } Limit 1000

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  DISTINCT  ?player { ?s foaf:page ?player. ?s rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/SoccerPlayer> . ?s dbpedia2:position ?position . ?s <http://dbpedia.org/property/clubs> ?club . ?club <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/capacity> ?cap . ?s <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> ?place . ?place ?population ?pop.  }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?name ?birth ?death ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {      ?person dbo:birthPlace :Berlin .      ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth .      ?person foaf:name ?name .      ?person dbo:deathDate ?death .      FILTER (?birth < "1900-01-01"^^xsd:date) . } ORDER BY ?name

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  DISTINCT  ?player { ?s foaf:name ?player. ?s rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/SoccerPlayer> . ?s dbpedia2:position ?position . ?s <http://dbpedia.org/property/clubs> ?club . ?club <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/capacity> ?cap . ?s <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> ?place . ?place ?population ?pop. OPTIONAL {?s <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/number> ?tricot.} Filter (?population in (<http://dbpedia.org/property/populationEstimate>, <http://dbpedia.org/property/populationCensus>, <http://dbpedia.org/property/statPop> )) Filter (xsd:int(?pop) >10000000 ) . Filter (xsd:int(?cap) <40000 ) . Filter (?position = "Goalkeeper"@en || ?position = <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goalkeeper_%28association_football%29> || ?position = <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goalkeeper_%28football%29>) } Limit 1000

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> CONSTRUCT { ?s ?p ?o }  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   ?s <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Richard Henry Lee"@en ; ?p ?o .    ?s dbpedia2:birthDate ?bdate .   FILTER(STRSTARTS(str(?bdate),"1732"))   ?s dbpedia2:deathDate ?ddate .   FILTER(STRSTARTS(str(?ddate),"1794")) }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?name ?birth ?description ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {      ?person dbo:birthPlace :Germany.      ?person <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:German_musicians> .      ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth .      ?person foaf:name ?name .      ?person rdfs:comment ?description .      FILTER (LANG(?description) = 'en') . } ORDER BY ?name

column2: dbpedia-owl:abstract ?abstract.

column1: SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   values ?resource { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dialog_system> }    ?resource dbpedia-owl:abstract ?abstract .   ?resource rdfs:comment ?comment .    filter (lang(?abstract), "en") .   filter (lang(?comment), "en") . }
SELECT  distinct ?Concept from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {[] a ?Concept} LIMIT 100

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>   SELECT  distinct ?label from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordian_III> rdfs:label ?label .   }

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>   SELECT  distinct ?sameAs ?label from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordian_III> owl:sameAs ?sameAs . ?sameAs rdfs:label ?label  }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>  SELECT  DISTINCT ?category ?label COUNT(?o) AS ?numOfInstances  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?category rdfs:label ?label .  ?label bif:contains "'Seoul'" .  ?o dcterms:subject ?category .  FILTER (lang(?label) = 'en' || lang(?label) = '') } ORDER BY DESC(?numOfInstances) LIMIT 30

SELECT  ?type ?class ?labelOfType ?labelOfClass COUNT(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?numOfInstances from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  ?s dcterms:subject <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:East_Asia> . ?s ?type ?o . ?o dcterms:subject ?class . ?type rdfs:label ?labelOfType . ?class rdfs:label ?labelOfClass . FILTER (lang(?labelOfClass) = 'en') } ORDER BY DESC(?numOfInstances) LIMIT 40

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?film from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?film <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> ?p }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?person from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?person foaf:name <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Living_people> .    } LIMIT 100

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?person ?name from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?person foaf:name ?name . } order ?name LIMIT 1000

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?person ?name from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?person foaf:name ?name . } order ?name

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?person ?name from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?person foaf:name ?name . } ORDER BY ?name LIMIT 1000

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?name from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?name foaf:name <"ABBA Live"@en> }  LIMIT 1000

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?relation ?entityRelated from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/snorql/?describe=http%3A//dbpedia.org/resource/ABBA> ?relation ?entityRelated }  LIMIT 1000

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  ?pais ?lat ?long from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {   ?pais rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Country>.   ?pais geo:lat ?lat FILTER (datatype(?lat) = xsd:float && (?lat-0.2273363048115043) < 0.005 && (-0.2273363048115043-?lat) < 0.005).  ?pais geo:long ?long FILTER (datatype(?long) = xsd:float && (?long-78.892578125) < 0.005 && (-78.892578125-?long) < 0.005) }

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?entityRelated from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABBA> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/recordLabel> ?entityRelated }  LIMIT 1000

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  ?relation  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Beatles> ?relation <http://dbpedia.org/resource/recordLabel> }

SELECT  DISTINCT ?Influences from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {{?auteur rdfs:label "Emily Gravett"@fr} UNION {?auteur foaf:name "Emily Gravett"@fr}.{{?auteur dbpedia-owl:influenced ?influence} UNION {?auteur dbpprop:influenced ?influence} UNION {?influence dbpedia-owl:influencedBy ?auteur} UNION {?influence dbpprop:influences ?auteur}}{?influence rdfs:label ?Influences}.FILTER (LANG(?Influences) = "fr")}

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ... }
SELECT  distinct ?book ?isbn from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE{?book dbpprop:name "Dream of the Red Chamber"@en. optional {?book dbpprop:isbn ?isbn.}}

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT   ?n  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?person foaf:name <"Eric Clapton"@en> .         ?person ?n <http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Beatles>    }order by ?name

PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>  PREFIX dbpowl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>  PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>   SELECT  DISTINCT ?name ?longName ?capital ?language from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?variable rdf:type dbpowl:Country . ?variable rdfs:label 'China'@en. OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:longName ?longName . FILTER (LANG(?longName)='en') } OPTIONAL{ ?variable rdfs:label ?name . FILTER (LANG(?name)='en') } OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:officialLanguage ?lang . ?lang foaf:name ?language . FILTER (LANG(?language)='en') }  OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:capital ?cap . ?cap rdfs:label ?capital . FILTER (LANG(?capital)='en') } } LIMIT 1

PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>  PREFIX dbpowl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>  PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>   SELECT  DISTINCT ?name ?longName ?capital ?language ?president from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?variable rdf:type dbpowl:Country . ?variable rdfs:label 'Spain'@en. OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:longName ?longName .  FILTER (LANG(?longName)='en') } OPTIONAL{ ?variable rdfs:label ?name . FILTER (LANG(?name)='en') } OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:officialLanguage ?lang . ?lang foaf:name ?language . FILTER (LANG(?language)='en') }  OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:capital ?cap . ?cap rdfs:label ?capital . FILTER (LANG(?capital)='en') }  OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:leaderTitle 'President'@en . ?variable dbpowl:leaderName ?p . ?p rdfs:label ?president . FILTER (LANG(?president)='en') } } LIMIT 1

PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>  PREFIX dbpowl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>  PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>   SELECT  DISTINCT ?name ?longName ?capital ?language ?president ?currency from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?variable rdf:type dbpowl:Country . ?variable rdfs:label 'China'@en. OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:longName ?longName .  FILTER (LANG(?longName)='en') } OPTIONAL{ ?variable rdfs:label ?name . FILTER (LANG(?name)='en') } OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:officialLanguage ?lang . ?lang foaf:name ?language . FILTER (LANG(?language)='en') }  OPTIONAL{ ?variable dbpowl:capital ?cap . ?cap rdfs:label ?capital . PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>  SELECT  distinct *from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {    ?uri ?b <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Book>. ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/isbn> ?isbn. ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/abstract> ?description.?uri rdfs:label ?title1.?uri foaf:depiction ?cover.?uri rdfs:comment ?comment.?uri foaf:name ?title2.?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/author> ?author.?author foaf:name ?name1.?author dbpedia-owl:birthName ?name2.?author dbpprop:name ?name3.FILTER(lang(?title1)="en" && lang(?title2)="en" && lang(?comment)="en" && lang(?name1)="en" && lang(?description)="en" && lang(?name2)="en" && lang(?name2)="en").} limit 100

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>         PREFIX type: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>   SELECT  DISTINCT ?planet ?planet_name  ?satellite ?satellite_name ?satellite_description ?satellite_picture from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  ?planet a dbp:Planet, dbp:CelestialBody;    rdfs:label ?planet_name.    #prop:satellites ?satellites.    ?satellite a dbp:CelestialBody;    rdfs:label ?satellite_name;    prop:satelliteOf ?satellite_of.    OPTIONAL { ?satellite dbp:abstract ?satellite_description. }    OPTIONAL { ?satellite dbp:thumbnail ?satellite_picture. }    FILTER(?satellite_of = ?planet)  FILTER(langMatches(lang(?satellite_name), "EN"))  FILTER(?satellite_of = ?planet)  FILTER(langMatches(lang(?planet_name), "EN"))  FILTER(langMatches(lang(?satellite_name), "EN"))  FILTER(langMatches(lang(?satellite_description), "EN"))  #FILTER(bif:contains(?planet_name, "Mars"@en))  #FILTER(?satellites > 0) } ORDER BY (?planet)

OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:position ?owl_position } . OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:number ?number} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpprop:currentpositionplain ?prop_position} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:weight ?weight} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpedia-owl:height ?height} . OPTIONAL {?player dbpprop:placeOfBirth ?place_of_birth} . # 2 -  SELECT  ALL THE TRIPLES ASSOCIATED TO ALL THE PROPERTIES I'M INTERESTED IN REFERRING TO THE MOVIES I  SELECT ED  SELECT  distinct ?m ?p ?o from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  ?m ?p ?o.  filter(regex(?p,"^http://dbpedia.org/ontology/")) .  # WE ARE NOT INTERSTED IN THE ABSTRACT (FOR TF-IDF OR JACCARD)  minus {?m dbpedia-owl:abstract ?o}.  minus {?m dbpedia-owl:thumbnail ?o}.  {  # 1 -  SELECT  THE MOVIES I'M INTERESTED IN    SELECT  distinct ?m   from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE   {    ?m dcterms:subject ?o.    dbpedia:The_Matrix dcterms:subject ?o.    ?m a dbpedia-owl:Film.   }   order by ?m
column2: # WE LIMIT TO 100 MOVIES JUST FOR THIS EXAMPLE   limit 100  # 1 -  } } order by ?m # 2 -

column2: # WE LIMIT TO 100 MOVIES JUST FOR THIS EXAMPLE   limit 100  # 1 -  } } order by ?m # 2 -

# 2 -  SELECT  ALL THE TRIPLES ASSOCIATED TO ALL THE PROPERTIES I'M INTERESTED IN REFERRING TO THE MOVIES I  SELECT ED  SELECT  distinct ?m ?p ?o from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  {    ?m ?p ?o.    filter(regex(?p,"^http://dbpedia.org/ontology/")) .    # WE ARE NOT INTERSTED IN THE ABSTRACT (FOR TF-IDF OR JACCARD)    minus {?m dbpedia-owl:abstract ?o}.    minus {?m dbpedia-owl:thumbnail ?o}.    minus {?m dbpedia-owl:wikiPageExternalLink ?o.}    minus     {            ?m ?p ?o.            ?p a owl:DatatypeProperty .    }  }  union  {    ?m dcterms:subject ?o .    ?m dcterms:subject/skos:broader ?o  }    {     # 1 -  SELECT  THE MOVIES I'M INTERESTED IN (THAT SHARE SOMETHING WITH dbpedia:The_Matrix)      SELECT  distinct ?m     from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE     {       ?m dcterms:subject ?o.       dbpedia:The_Matrix dcterms:subject ?o.       ?m a dbpedia-owl:Film.     }     order by ?m
column2: # WE LIMIT TO 100 MOVIES JUST FOR THIS EXAMPLE     limit 100    # 1 -    } } order by ?m # 2 -

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>  SELECT  * from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?city a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Place>; rdfs:label 'Angosto'@nn.  ?airport a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Airport>. {?airport <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/city> ?city} UNION {?airport <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> ?city} UNION {?airport <http://dbpedia.org/property/cityServed> ?city.} UNION {?airport <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/city> ?city. }{?airport <http://dbpedia.org/property/iata> ?iata.} UNION  {?airport <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/iataLocationIdentifier> ?iata. } OPTIONAL { ?airport foaf:homepage ?airport_home. } OPTIONAL { ?airport rdfs:label ?name. } OPTIONAL { ?airport <http://dbpedia.org/property/nativename> ?airport_name.} FILTER ( !bound(?name) || langMatches( lang(?name), 'nn') )}

FILTER (contains(str(?geonameid), "geonames")) }   OPTIONAL { ?c  foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?wiki . }   FILTER ( lang(?name) = "en"  && ( ?type = <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/City> || ?type = <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Town> ) ) } LIMIT 1000

column1: PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>  SELECT  DISTINCT ?category ?label COUNT(?o) AS ?numOfInstances  from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE { ?category rdfs:label ?label .  ?label bif:contains "'german 'and' physicists'" .  ?o dcterms:subject ?category .  FILTER (lang(?label) = 'en' || lang(?label) = '') } ORDER BY DESC(?numOfInstances) LIMIT 30

SELECT  ?type ?class ?labelOfType ?labelOfClass COUNT(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?numOfInstances from <http://dbpedia3.8>  WHERE {  ?s dcterms:subject <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:German_physicists> . ?s ?type ?o . ?o dcterms:subject ?class . ?type rdfs:label ?labelOfType . ?class rdfs:label ?labelOfClass . FILTER (lang(?labelOfClass) = 'en') } ORDER BY DESC(?numOfInstances) LIMIT 40
